{"tid":8450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"送咩禮物比男仔好","createTime":"2016-11-28T11:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T14:02:50.000Z","uid":374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0af049048c84972a86711987e292d0fdccdf536e","tid":8450,"uid":374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T11:27:16.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n有個男仔因為幫過佢少少野送左盒好貴（~100$）嘅朱古力比我（其實佢本來想送平野 但因為d小意外買左盒貴嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n貴到我都唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以覺得要送翻d野比佢<br />\n但大家係普通fd 送翻朱古力怕尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d6115da1ae11186a01f9ff1e88b65508cce670","tid":8450,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T11:29:41.000Z","msg":"佢有冇啲咩興趣？"},{"pid":"fe4bf49413f1eccec84ae780d1477edd1aa8d5f0","tid":8450,"uid":4725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T11:34:26.000Z","msg":"Condom+KY <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35299870f95daf14a4a2e4c0974f5495800f3307","tid":8450,"uid":9076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T11:43:12.000Z","msg":"自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2a722e51ca61b698641cf87f1f6cea9052f05b","tid":8450,"uid":374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T11:44:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢有冇啲咩興趣？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係好知 都係啱啱識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cbd532a526d632b9f91f283612117c15f05f3f2","tid":8450,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11